Avatar of ThePodfather
Spotify
ThePodfather
Spotify
2025-08-14 09:19 AM
Hey! Thanks so much for your feedback and for sharing your experience with Daylist.

 

At the moment, there isn’t a way to manually reset or refresh your Daylist recommendations. The Daylist updates automatically throughout the day based on your recent listening habits, and the titles are generated by Spotify’s algorithms. If you’d like your Daylist to reflect different moods or genres, the best way is to explore and listen to a variety of music over time, this will help influence future Daylist updates.

 

Regarding the use of words like “gay,” “lesbian,” or “queer” in Daylist or DJ titles: We appreciate your suggestion and understand how important representation is. We’re always working to make Spotify more inclusive, and your feedback is really valuable. I’ll make sure to pass this along to the right team.If you have any more suggestions or want to share additional feedback, please let us know!

